&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Product Managers and Engineers to translate product requirements into thoughtful, user-centered solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create user flows, wireframes, prototypes, and high-fidelity designs using Figma.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Engineering throughout development to ensure a seamless, high-quality implementation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct user research and usability testing, using customer feedback and data to continuously improve the product experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to and evolve our design system, ensuring consistency and scalability across the platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advocate for the user while balancing technical constraints and business goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Requirements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of experience as a Product Designer in a B2B SaaS company. Experience working at a cybersecurity company is a strong advantage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience designing complex products or platforms from concept to launch.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong portfolio demonstrating UX thinking, interaction design, and visual design across end-to-end product experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with Figma and modern prototyping tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working closely with Product Managers and Engineering teams in an agile environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solving skills with a user-first mindset and exceptional attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and presentation skills, with the ability to clearly articulate design decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing products for technical users, developers, cloud infrastructure, or cybersecurity environments is an advantage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to thrive in a fast-paced startup environment with a high level of ownership and autonomy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

